# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# Unneeded for Build. The bare `node_modules` pattern only matches at the
# context root, so nested ones (packages/*/node_modules) leak in unless we
# also glob them explicitly — and on a dev machine those contain stale
# symlinks into ~/.bun/install that resolve to nothing inside the image.
node_modules
**/node_modules
*.local
dev
eslint.config.js
LICENSE
*.md
.gitignore
components.json
.claude
.github
README.md

